description: This is security trap. Security traps are reported
according to value of f3SecurityTrapType object.
This trap is sent every time a privilege change request is changed (added, modified, removed).
tests: $SNMPTRAPCMD CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTrap CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeState i 5 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeUserName s EXAMPLE CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeIpv4Address a 192.0.2.1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeIpv6Address s EXAMPLEEXAMPLEEX CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTerminalIpv4Address a 192.0.2.1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTerminalIpv6Address s EXAMPLEEXAMPLEEX CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeInterface i 1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeCurrentPrivilege i 0 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeRequestedPrivilege i 0 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeDuration u 1

$SNMPTRAPCMD CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTrap CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeState i 4 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeUserName s EXAMPLE CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeIpv4Address a 192.0.2.1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeIpv6Address s EXAMPLEEXAMPLEEX CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTerminalIpv4Address a 192.0.2.1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTerminalIpv6Address s EXAMPLEEXAMPLEEX CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeInterface i 1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeCurrentPrivilege i 0 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeRequestedPrivilege i 0 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeDuration u 1

$SNMPTRAPCMD CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTrap CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeState i 2 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeUserName s EXAMPLE CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeIpv4Address a 192.0.2.1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeIpv6Address s EXAMPLEEXAMPLEEX CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTerminalIpv4Address a 192.0.2.1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeTerminalIpv6Address s EXAMPLEEXAMPLEEX CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeInterface i 1 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeCurrentPrivilege i 0 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeRequestedPrivilege i 0 CM-SECURITY-MIB::f3PrivilegeChangeDuration u 1
